OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and rather
OL,6,Fbreezy this morning with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading northeastwards. Wind
OL,8,Fand rain easing and skies brightening
OL,9,Fthis afternoon, but scattered slow
OL,10,Fmoving showers also developing. These
OL,11,Fcould be heavy and possibly thundery
OL,12,Fat times.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers slowly fading away
OL,15,Fwith skies largely clearing during the
OL,16,Fsecond half of the night. Some gusty
OL,17,Fwinds likely at times overnight,
OL,18,Fparticularly over hills and near
OL,19,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
